Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.33,0:00:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,拳擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,跟學長借的第一神拳\N讓我對拳擊開始有興趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真不該借她的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,來當我的對手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會打拳擊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你只要站著被我打就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我是沙包嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,拳擊手不能在場外打人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.83,0:00:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你放心 我會點到為止的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩也可以打回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.41,0:01:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,打啊打啊 學長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你打到我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,她會殺了我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然使出扭抱招式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真有學長的行事風格
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,事情就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,學長突然使出扭抱招式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.91,0:02:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,噁心到笑死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,扭抱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好糟糕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,扭抱是很正規的戰術耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想扭抱學長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.29,0:02:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我 比起扭抱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我更想試試寢技
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,投降投降
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,拳擊裡沒有寢技
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,試一下也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我們現在去找學長練拳擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.04,0:02:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,拳擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以在場外打人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.95,0:02:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那你算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:03:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我自有分寸 所以沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也很有分寸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,(美術教室)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,學長 你快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,學長 陪我練拳擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-扭抱\N-寢技
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,學長 這裡交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 要上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然她說了很帥的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但也是因她而起的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不要胡鬧 (Easy)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,捉弄胡鬧 的Everyday (Easy)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是否越來越接近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼反應 沒寫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:04:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我在意的不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,能量活力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,「女孩子就應該這樣那樣」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,妄想 願望 都只是空想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,快點 絞盡腦汁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,想一直贏過你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不要反擊喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,壓倒性的完全勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,因為喜歡 所以為所欲為
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,想破壞一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy Love (Easy Love)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy Love (Night Date)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 只有你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,還不清楚 青澀的春日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,清醒的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy Love (Easy Love)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy Love (Night Date)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy Love (Easy Love)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是愛的形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不要胡鬧 (Easy)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不要執著 (Easy)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,捉弄胡鬧Everyday (Easy)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們大聲喧囂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,(學長是悶騷鬼！！)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我的休憩場所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,在社團教室 一個人靜靜畫圖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,畫圖…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,(美術教室)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,裸體 裸體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,全裸耶 畫上衣服啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,很藝術啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是學長耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-歡迎\N-我的休憩場所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好\N-被侵略了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼特來我的社團教室胡鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我們平常都在學校食堂吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但最近有群傢伙在那裡喧譁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你們的聲音有點大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.37,0:06:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,提醒過了仍然很吵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我們決定在這裡吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是美術社耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我好意外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你們竟然就這樣乖乖離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為你們會強迫他們閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,學長 太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:07:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,比起強迫他們 還有更好的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,更好的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,讓刺客 混入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡應該要存檔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你們在玩什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,玩遊戲嗎 也教教我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒喔 你好會教人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,沒 沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 下次我們一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好帥喔 我好像喜歡上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.91,0:07:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你有交往的對象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,沒… 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不到一星期
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他們就會從內部開始瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,然後我們就能回學校食堂用餐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,學長就可以放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,男人都是無法抵抗性慾的可悲生物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,可悲生物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,儘量不要與這些人為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可是學長看起來沒什麼性慾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來是草食系男子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,綿羊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不 學長的性慾很明顯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,隨便逗弄他 他就臉紅心跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你在胡說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,學長 來親親吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,親…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.83,0:08:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 他以為自己會被親\N所以臉都紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,因為學長是個悶騷鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不 那是處男的特有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,草食系男子 無性慾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們來打賭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼賭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這間教室裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,藏起來的色色書刊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,找到就算我贏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,輸的人要請吃鬆餅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣 我接受挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡沒有色色書刊啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你的反應很可疑喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,(實況轉播)\N你覺得如何呢 小鴨解說員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他是無辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩選手只是看起來形跡可疑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他是怕被發現色色書刊而慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能 絕對不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有 絕對有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,色色書刊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不能說沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,後宮樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,在青年雜誌上連載的漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,裡面… 幾乎是色色的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是喜歡八神倫太郎老師的\N精美畫風及傳統奇幻劇情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,絕不是為色色內容才看的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,而那本漫畫現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,正放在隔壁的準備室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 這間美術室裡並沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,色色書刊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多過了15分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,再怎麼找也沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對… 有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你差不多該認輸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,學長就是草食系男子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,草食系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,快點認輸吧 學長就是綿羊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,綿羊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,長瀞 真是遺憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,美術室裡當然沒有色色書刊囉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,找到色色書刊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,噁心 變態…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,噁心 變態…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-走吧\N-走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,(不要欺負我，長瀞同學)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(噁心學長怎麼可能會約會)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,學長好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,耳環
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你又在畫無聊的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,還… 挺適合你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝學長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,太久沒戴 耳洞都合起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:13:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就用這個 重新打了耳洞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一點都不痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,只是稍微刺刺的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,學長也戴個耳針吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你怕痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不是痛不痛的問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我突然戴耳針很怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不怪不怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,覺得害羞的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就只在房間裡戴吧 如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我戴成對的耳針喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,成對的耳針…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,別動 很危險喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,只有刺刺的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不…等…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 我破身了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,長瀞害我嫁不出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是捏了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,學長怎麼一副遺憾的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.33,0:14:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我… 我哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,其實你很想戴耳針吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,痛… 我才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,學長… 救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,(家庭餐廳)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,跟蹤狂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算擾亂那群人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但其中一人變成跟蹤狂\N拚命騷擾你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好糟喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,糟喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,現在也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,學長 你覺得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,自作自受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,誰叫你們要玩弄別人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,學長惹人家哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:16:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,學長… 我有事想拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可以假裝… 當我的男朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他看到我們卿卿我我的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他應該就會放棄了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要我假裝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,人家現在沒對象
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,能拜託的對象只剩學長了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,假裝男朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這招不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,反正學長人畜無害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,人畜無害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不 有害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他超有害的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,比害蟲還要有害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.83,0:16:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你以為找噁心學長假裝男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就能擺脫跟蹤狂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,跟蹤狂會變雙倍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:16:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你胡說八道什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不會做那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那就麻煩學長 假裝我的男朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,沒差 可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,(逗子車站)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,勉強答應了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,可是約會要做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,反正只是假裝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,隨便亂晃就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 等很久了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不… 沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:17:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,學長很緊張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不… 沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,今天由我主導
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,主導
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,學長形跡太可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這種情景\N像不像學長喜歡的動畫劇情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.75,0:18:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,像喔像喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,兩人因某種原因假裝約會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,假裝約會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,卻不小心過於入戲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,氣氛漸漸變好…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,變好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,最後就假戲真做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,變成真正的約會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的約會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他才不會約什麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你生什麼氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然是我拜託學長的\N但這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒有想約會的對象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,沒…沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來 跟蹤狂人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好像沒看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛 好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,長瀞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 我不會再犯了 請饒了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這場鬧劇…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,該結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好戲沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,早點解決問題是好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,可是… 沒拍到精采鏡頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,精采鏡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼精采鏡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有機可趁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.62,0:20:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 我不會再犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我們也回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,學長 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,學長 真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你期待已久的初次約會泡湯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,沒差… 反正是假裝約會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,正好少了一樁麻煩事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你在想糟糕事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,想跟人牽手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不小心碰人家胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,或是運氣好的話\N就能擺脫處男的身分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕 學長好糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我才沒這麼想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,對學長來說 約會這種事還太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,也是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,學長果然很噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.04,0:22:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就算每天聊個沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,話題仍聊不完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天遇到的所有事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.79,0:22:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,都想告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.29,0:22:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,最近(學長)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.41,0:22:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,比以前(學長)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,增加許多(學長)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒發現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,一如往常 放學後在美術室集合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.45,0:22:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嘻笑打鬧 就跟平常一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:23:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,漸漸地變化 描繪著校園的容貌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,明天比今天 變得更加繽紛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.83,0:23:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的反省重點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.91,0:23:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,學長 找色色書刊時你作斃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,作弊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.33,0:23:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.54,0:23:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,既然都到這個地步了\N你們趕快交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.83,0:23:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,小吉 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.91,0:23:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.83,0:23:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,來… 來欺負我啊
